description: This truck is serving up a menu that is as satisfyingly simple as its name. Whether you’re in the mood for fantastic fried fish or the best ¼ pound burger, you just choose the right combo for you, and joyously dig into this delicious food. They’re also totally crushin’ it with their amazing Cherry and Raspberry Grape Slushies, they’re a local fave. You must hear Raleigh’s rallying cry and make Food Delicious the next truck you try!
name: Food Delicious
